Class MarcXmlFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xml.sax.helpers.XMLFilterImpl
      • org.marc4j.marcxml.ExtendedFilter
        • org.marc4j.marcxml.MarcXmlFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MarcHandler, ContentHandler, DTDHandler, EntityResolver, ErrorHandler, LexicalHandler, XMLFilter, XMLReader
    @Deprecated
public class MarcXmlFilter
extends ExtendedFilter
implements MarcHandler
    Deprecated.
    This class has been replaced by MarcXmlReader

    MarcXmlFilter is an XMLFilter that consumes MarcHandler events and reports events to a SAX2 ContentHandler.

    Author:
    Bas Peters
